# The feed scene: sum-typed elements. expect_order reads the For
# container's bare label children — only the Note case stamps one, so
# the order reads the notes; todo rows nest theirs. Promote converts
# the first note into a finished todo: same key, restamped in place,
# so a note leaves the order and the done count rises.
settle 300
expect_order column#0 "jot one|jot two"
expect label#0 "0 done"
toggle checkbox#0 on
settle 200
expect label#0 "1 done"
click button#0
settle 200
expect_order column#0 "jot two"
expect label#0 "2 done"
toggle checkbox#1 off
settle 200
expect label#0 "1 done"
